OL,3,CReform's new leader in Wales proves he
OL,4,Cis eligible to vote in the country
OL,6,FReform's new leader in Wales says he
OL,7,Fhas proof he is eligible to vote in
OL,8,Fthe country.
OL,10,FIn a letter seen by ITV Cymru Wales,
OL,11,FDan Thomas is shown to have been added
OL,12,Fto the electoral register in
OL,13,FCaerphilly County Borough last year.
OL,15,FThe letter from electoral services
OL,16,Fconfirms he was registered in July
OL,17,F2025. He moved back to Wales in late
OL,18,F2024 but did not register to vote
OL,19,Funtil the following year.
