OL,3,CReform's new leader in Wales proves he
OL,4,Cis eligible to vote in the country
OL,6,FMr Thomas was unveiled on Thursday as
OL,7,FNigel Farage's choice to lead Reform
OL,8,FUK into the Senedd election.
OL,10,FThe former Conservative leader of
OL,11,FBarnet Council in north London, who
OL,12,Fwas born in Blackwood, has dismissed
OL,13,Freports that he does not live in Wales
OL,14,Fas "smear attempts".
OL,16,FOver the weekend, it was claimed Mr
OL,17,FThomas was living in a #1 million home
OL,18,Fin Bath. He later told the BBC that
OL,19,Fwhile he has a property portfolio, he
OL,20,Fand his family are now living in Wales.
